metadata.name: ZORG #1
metadata.description: THIS IS ZORG. HES RIGHTEOUSLY TRAVELLING THE OUTER SPACES AND HES LIT AF. HE GOT LOST WHILE TRAVELLING AND NOW HE NEEDS YOUR HELP TO NAVIGATE THE YONDERS. WHAT WILL HE ENCOUNTER. IF YOU OWN A ZORG YOU WILL HELP DECIDE WHERE HE GOES. THERE WILL BE 10 ORIGINAL ZORGS UP FOR AUCTION THROUGHOUT THIS MONTH. GET YOUR HANDS ON ONE!
